  "texts": [
    "Employing denoising algorithms and feature enhancement techniques is essential for improving the usability of these datasets, thereby facilitating more clear interpretations of paleontological findings.",
    "We explore novel image enhancement techniques to improve the clarity and interpretability of fossil images, enabling researchers to derive more accurate conclusions from the paleontological data.",
    "Automated image enhancement, targeting the optimization of brightness, contrast, and noise levels specific to each imaging modality, is a fundamental step of advanced fossil analysis.",
    "Integrating advanced image-processing techniques has significantly enhanced the analysis and interpretation in medical imaging (Landini et al. 2018; Dougherty 2011; Scholl et al. 2011) and satellite imagery (Varshney and Arora 2004; Asokan et al. 2020).",
    "In medical imaging (Akhtar et al. 2021; Rai et al. 2023), automated enhancement techniques adjust brightness and contrast to improve the visibility of anatomical structures in X-rays or MRIs."
